Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory206.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: 'Sorry. Must have woke you up.', 4: '1'}
{3: "Finished with the skirmish, Alpha returns to the bench to find Luna long awake. Luna merely shakes her head at Alpha's apology."}
{2: 'α', 3: "What's the matter? You're staring at me.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Ahaha... Nothing. It really fits you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: "Yeah. The texture is nice. I think it's some famous brand from the Golden Age. The design makes swinging my sword easy.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "That's not what I meant by fitting you.", 4: '1'}
{3: "Luna's words send Alpha into deep thought. Then suddenly, as if in realization, she opens her mouth and continues."}
{2: 'α', 3: "Well... Next time, if you want pictures of me, just say so. You don't have to take them secretly.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "That won't be the same.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "Well, it's late. Let's go back.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna rises from the bench and puts a jacket on Alpha, then turns and saunters through the road they came from.'}
{3: 'Alpha nods, and falls in step with Luna after accepting her jacket.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory206.png'}
{3: 'After Luna and Alpha left, a figure emerges from the shadows of the walkway.'}
{3: 'He gazes in the direction of the two and falls into deep thought.'}
